  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Developing the Foundation**\n\nI\'m working on building a professional online resume/portfolio for Wuttipong Sartsri. Based on prior information and an image, I have confirmed his name and date of birth: January 4, 1998. Now I am gathering additional insights to develop the content and design of the webpage.\n\n\n**Gathering Contact & Employment**\n\nI\'ve updated Wuttipong\'s age (he\'s 28 now) and collected his contact details: phone numbers, email, and address. I\'ve noted his current job title: Product Content Department Manager, starting April 2022. I\'m also adding new skills like UX/UI Design, Data Analysis, and AI-powered web app creation to his skill set, along with his existing proficiencies.\n\n\n**Compiling Qualifications & Plan**\n\nI\'ve incorporated Wuttipong\'s certificate details: Infographic Design (2020) and Creative Marketing (2020). Updated his employment history, noting Digital Content Writer (2021-March 2022) and Product Content Department Manager (April 2022-Present) at Home Product Center Pub Co., Ltd. or \"Current Company\" (need to clarify). The goal is a professional web app, highlighting design. I\'ve chosen React, Tailwind CSS, and Lucide React. I\'ve also outlined the structural components: Navigation, Hero, About, and Skills.\n\n\n**Structuring the Components**\n\nI\'m now organizing the webpage\'s content into key categories: Hard Skills, Soft Skills, Design & Tech. I\'ll present his experience as a job timeline, and education/certificates as a list. The portfolio will feature project cards in a grid format, and the footer will display contact information. I\'m aiming for a professional, clean design, with slate and charcoal color scheme and subtle indigo or teal accents. I\'ll be using `lucide-react` for the icons. I plan to build the single-view app in `src/App.tsx`. I\'ll start by updating the `metadata.json` and replacing existing boilerplate in `src/App.tsx` with the new design. I\'m now drafting the Hero section content, including his name and title.\n\n\n**Refining Wuttipong\'s Profile**\n\nI\'m focusing on crafting the \"About\" section and refining Wuttipong\'s narrative. I\'ll highlight his evolution from digital marketing to a tech-savvy professional, emphasizing expertise in UX/UI, data analytics, and AI web development. I am detailing his experience with quantifiable results and using strong action verbs to highlight accomplishments.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 9
      nanos: 332471179
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
